a_009.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=83d3d401\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_009.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_010.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Freviews%2F17%2Fnokia-8%2Fhandson%2Fcamera%2Fgsmarena_010.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=bc89437c\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_010.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_011.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Freviews%2F17%2Fnokia-8%2Fhandson%2Fcamera%2Fgsmarena_011.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c251f33d\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_011.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_012.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Freviews%2F17%2Fnokia-8%2Fhandson%2Fcamera%2Fgsmarena_012.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=413823fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_012.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_013.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Freviews%2F17%2Fnokia-8%2Fhandson%2Fcamera%2Fgsmarena_013.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=3fe093bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_013.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_014.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Freviews%2F17%2Fnokia-8%2Fhandson%2Fcamera%2Fgsmarena_014.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9c9a8439\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_014.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_015.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Freviews%2F17%2Fnokia-8%2Fhandson%2Fcamera%2Fgsmarena_015.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e2423478\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_015.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_016.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Freviews%2F17%2Fnokia-8%2Fhandson%2Fcamera%2Fgsmarena_016.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=612be4bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_016.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\nWe tried the Dual Sight option too. The image quality of the selfie camera seems stellar, but we found it strange that the resulting image is 8MP. How do you combine the photos from two 13MP cameras and end up with 8MP?<br />\n<br />\nPlus, since you have to take both shots simultaneously, framing is tricky. It would have been easier if it had the option to take the photo in two steps (as other camera apps have done in the past).<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_017.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Freviews%2F17%2Fnokia-8%2Fhandson%2Fcamera%2Fgsmarena_017.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=1ff354fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_017.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_018.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Freviews%2F17%2Fnokia-8%2Fhandson%2Fcamera%2Fgsmarena_018.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=fcaecdf6\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_018.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_019.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Freviews%2F17%2Fnokia-8%2Fhandson%2Fcamera%2Fgsmarena_019.jpg&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=82767db7\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/reviews/17/nokia-8/handson/camera/gsmarena_019.jpg</a><br />\nFinally, here are several 4K 2160p video samples we took. Keep in mind that the color sensor of the rear camera has optical image stabilization. Also, the Nokia 8 boasts three mics with special audio recording algorithms from OZO... but we think they could have done something to reduce wind noise.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4c9bXBJ7K6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4c9bXBJ7K6E&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f6d3ecc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4c9bXBJ7K6E</a><br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://www.gsmarena.com/nokia_8_hands_on-review-1641p4.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gsmarena.com%2Fnokia_8_hands_on-review-1641p4.php&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=603903d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gsmarena.com/nokia_8_hands_on-review-1641p4.php</a> (入面有其他評測)"},{"pid":"793aa28e70bd3de1c7448a4646a1837d5635d4b6","tid":363804,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:35:00.000Z","msg":"